24 year old Caucasian female, 5 feet 6 inches, 78.5 kilograms
Nova Scotia, Canada 
Currently suffering from eczema
Takes escitalopram and Wellbutrin for anxiety

I’ve had this black spot on my right foot for about a month. It started out as a blister that I got from walking. I have washed the dirt out and drained the fluid. Unfortunately, the spot is still there and now there are smaller spots forming next to it.

I have also filed and pumiced the area to no avail. At this point, I can’t tell if the spots are scabs or bruises. 

My foot does not hurt anymore but the black spots are starting to worry me.[Gross foot](https://www.instagram.com/p/B1BXv-QlNUSgSbYi7MB5slLOHZY2LS2QzjF8Xo0/?igshid=16pvlfxo1obcr)
